 "system": "openfrp74",
 "category": "system-rules",
 "description": "Only lowest-level characters can be hired: advertise by notices, public frequenting, or messengers to elf-land, dwarf-land and the like — at a cost and delay the referee sets — then tempt the respondent with an offer and roll 2d6 reaction. Monsters serve if of like alignment, or Charmed; a genuine reward must be offered (sparing a life is not one). Charisma caps the entourage.",
